    <item>
      <title>Super Micro 纳入标准普尔 500 指数推动涨势突破 1,000%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/super-micro-s-s-p-500-inclusion-pushes-rally-past-1-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司可能很快就会被另一家去年回报率惊人的人工智能相关公司取代，成为标准普尔 500 指数中表现最佳股票的宝座。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/super-micro-s-s-p-500-inclusion-pushes-rally-past-1-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:43:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默多克的新体育投资目标是吸引 500 万订阅者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/murdoch-targets-5-million-subscribers-for-new-sports-tv-venture</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福克斯公司首席执行官拉克兰·默多克表示，他将于今年晚些时候与华特迪士尼公司和华纳兄弟探索公司推出的新体育流媒体服务预计五年后将达到 500 万订户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/murdoch-targets-5-million-subscribers-for-new-sports-tv-venture</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:56:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 和 Salesforce 签署承诺，打造人工智能造福人类</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/openai-salesforce-sign-pledge-to-build-ai-for-good-of-humanity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI、Salesforce Inc. 和其他科技公司签署了一封公开信，强调了“最大限度地发挥人工智能的好处并降低风险”对社会的“集体责任”，这是科技行业呼吁负责任地构建人工智能的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/openai-salesforce-sign-pledge-to-build-ai-for-good-of-humanity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citizens首席执行官Van Saun：人工智能是市场的首要考虑因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-04/citizens-ceo-van-saun-ai-is-top-of-mind-for-the-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公民金融集团董事长兼首席执行官 Bruce Van Saun 与 Ed Ludlow 和 Caroline Hyde 一起讨论了该公司如何将人工智能融入其运营、Reddit IPO 以及一年前硅谷银行倒闭的教训。他在“彭博科技”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-04/citizens-ceo-van-saun-ai-is-top-of-mind-for-the-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Razor Group 在亚马逊“聚合器”洗牌中收购 Perch</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/arnault-backed-razor-buys-perch-in-amazon-aggregator-shakeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于柏林的 Razor Group 正在以全股票交易的方式收购总部位于波士顿的 Perch，加速了“聚合商”的整合，这些“聚合商”抢购了流行的在线品牌，结果却眼睁睁地看着大流行引发的销售热潮消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/arnault-backed-razor-buys-perch-in-amazon-aggregator-shakeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩表示，如果董事会被罢免，将考虑对 SoftwareOne 进行新的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/bain-said-to-mull-fresh-bid-for-softwareone-if-board-is-ousted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果瑞士 SoftwareOne Holding AG 的创始股东下个月成功罢免董事会，贝恩资本有兴趣再次尝试收购这家公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/bain-said-to-mull-fresh-bid-for-softwareone-if-board-is-ousted</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:25:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
